        public final boolean hasOffset()
        Has the field been laid out in the object yet ?
        Returns:

      • getOffset

        public final Offset getOffset()
        Offset of this field or method, in bytes.
        • For a static field: offset of field from start of jtoc
        • For a static method: offset of code object reference from start of jtoc
        • For a non-static field: offset of field from start of object
        • For a non-static method: offset of code object reference from start of tib
        Returns:
        offset in bytes as described above

      • setOffset

        Only meant to be used by ObjectModel.layoutInstanceFields. TODO: refactor system so this functionality is in the classloader package and this method doesn't have to be final.
        Parameters:
        off - new offset for this member
